Comment: 0,0:26:06.92,0:26:06.96,Dialogue,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dacă eroii, care au salvat lumea, \Nși-ar fi putut găsi pacea,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.69,0:00:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}misiunea lor ar fi fost terminată acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.19,0:00:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar acei eroi au fost denunțați și condamnați la moarte de către cei pe care-i salvaseră cândva.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.99,0:00:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oamenii care au spus că nu mai aveau nevoie de acei titani foarte puternici.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.01,0:00:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar asta era greșit.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eroii care au făcut fapte legendare
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.93,0:01:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nu ar trebui să aibă parte \Nde o moarte așa de crudă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.93,0:01:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dacă erau omorâți în timp ce încă erau eroi,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}atunci reveneau la viață \Nca niște cetățeni obișnuiți.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.63,0:01:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ajutarea eroilor în a deveni niște cetățeni obișnuiți,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.24,0:01:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}asta era treaba Agenției de Pensionare a Eroilor și Revenire la Viața de Zi cu Zi.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eroi gemeni?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.29,0:02:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surori care au fost trimise împreună,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,au lucrat împreună și s-au întors împreună ca eroi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios? Asta chiar e ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numele surorii mai mari este Tsuranari Hakua.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.64,0:02:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar sora mai mică este Kougyoku.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.90,0:02:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci de care mă voi ocupa eu?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sora mai mare? Sau cea mai mică?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amândouă.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.93,0:02:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amândouă?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.84,0:02:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.70,0:02:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Din moment ce e un caz așa de rar, am hotărât ca amândouă să tranziteze împreună la o viață obișnuită.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar ca această misiune \Npericuloasă să-ți revină ție, Uro,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a fost o decizie unanimă.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.84,0:02:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superiorii chiar cred că este în regulă să-mi dea orice misiune doresc ei?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu poți refuza și nici nu te poți scoate.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-ar păcea măcar să primesc niște scuze.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.63,0:02:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ceea ce înseamnă că de acum,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.00,0:02:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,voi două veți trăi aici pe Pământ ca niște cetățeni obișnuiți.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.73,0:02:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aveți vreo întrebare?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă avem vreo întrebare, auzi la el.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.76,0:03:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mai întâi, trebuie să faci o plecăciune, om de rând!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este nepoliticos să vorbești de la același nivel ca și mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.12,0:03:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am mai spus asta, dar nu mai sunteți eroi, ci niște persoane obișnuite.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De acum înainte, va trebui să învățați și să munciți ca restul oamenilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să-i spui unui cavaler că este o "persoană obșinuită" este foarte enervant.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.66,0:03:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă eu sunt o persoană obișnuită, atunci tu ce ești? Un vierme?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sau poate un gunoi?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mă voi schimba!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sfidătoare ca întotdeauna.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.15,0:03:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, copii ca tine se adaptează repede la viața de zi cu zi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, sigur.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-o crezi tu că mă voi trăi \Nprintre oamenii de rând.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa, surioară?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.49,0:03:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu sabia, armura și \Nornamentele pe care le-am făcut,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sora mea va fi mereu un erou...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu se va schimba niciodată.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt sigură de asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-am întors!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.80,0:04:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, am avut atât de multe de făcut la muncă! Dar am dat {\i1}tot {\i0}ce am putut!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uro, pregătește cina!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bună treabă.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently you've been doing full shifts every day.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.53,0:04:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to build up experience \Nquickly so I can level up my skills!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't keep being a bother to the shop manager forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How admirable of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.40,0:04:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with me there, the atmosphere of the shop has improved, so I can rise quickly.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there is something I want.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.29,0:04:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be able to get it \Nif I save up just a little more.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't work yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just an ordinary person now—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm tired of hearing that!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.42,0:04:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time. They say it's good to keep a goal in mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.79,0:04:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sister of mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear my talk?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's your pride as a hero?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you getting so upset about?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.54,0:04:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not as though I can avoid\N rubbing shoulders with the masses,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean\N I have given up my pride.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.36,0:05:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way home from work at the café, \NI got a little cake so cutesy you'd squeal!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand... what are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's with that ordinary outfit?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the silver armor I gave you?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.83,0:05:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, I'd feel out of place wearing that!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try being fashionable?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's tons of cute clothing in this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku, you should join us next time we—
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the sword? \NThe sword I gave you!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Don't you know?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The earth has this legal system.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.51,0:05:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll arrest you if you\N have a blade over 6 cm long.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A law?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And gems?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the ruby in which I instilled divine protection?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I wore that it would get stolen!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't get shot, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And anyway, there's no \Nsuch thing as demons in this world,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I don't need divine protection.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.10,0:06:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not my sister anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kougyoku.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take off that eyepatch.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you can actually see.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably dangerous to \Nnot have depth perception.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with that attitude?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uro, hurry up and make dinner.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.06,0:06:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the floor's sopping wet! Wipe that up!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat dinner?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't like ginger roast?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you making a weapon?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.60,0:07:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's what you've \Nbeen doing your whole life.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.16,0:07:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The days keep coming, and you keep working in your studio,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making weapons and \Narmor and protective ornaments.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All for Hakua.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't it hard for you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.02,0:07:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That no matter how much work you put into the weapons,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.87,0:07:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only one who received the honor and praise was the hero Hakua?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you're the \None who gave Hakua her power,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no one paid any attention to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.14,0:07:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just keep giving, but you can't get anything in return.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the fate of a supporting character.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.65,0:07:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the crowds speak of Hakua,\N my swords and armor are included.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is my pride.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need any reward.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly why it's so hard \Nfor me to forgive Hakua for changing.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tossing away the things\N I've made so carefully,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for some "part-time job", for some "fashion"!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you changing my Hakua?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamada Uro!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.59,0:08:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you made Hakua into a hero,\N I'll make you two into regular citizens.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't change!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of that I am sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll show you, \Nand make Hakua a hero again!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that sword's all bent.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.14,0:08:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's proof you're not looking at what's in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't make a weapon that way.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.89,0:08:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the world you want to be in, \Nyou can't easily use magic here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.33,0:08:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to become a craftsperson in this world, it'd be best to start from scratch—
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I use it that way, it's a weapon.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... huh.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.72,0:09:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuranari Kougyoku. Former craftsperson.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.62,0:09:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Item-maker who used all of her\N power for her older sister, a hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like she's still trapped in a dream.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that dream is probably...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking so gloomy?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.06,0:09:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't forgive the world that takes\N the sister that she gave her all to,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and turns her into something mediocre, isn't she just the model younger sister?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh, how innocent...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.35,0:09:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having dreams is an admirable thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.01,0:09:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd like if she'd stop having her dreams depend on another person.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.65,0:09:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's entrusting her \Nentire worth as a person to her sister...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a fool.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should try to arrange a little get-together?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get-together?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.24,0:09:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assemble Alice and the heroes you've worked with so far at the beach,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.78,0:10:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and let Kougyoku-chan meet \Nsomeone other than Hakua-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can count on me to be there to help.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good idea,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you're not just asking because \Nyou want to see girls in swimsuits, are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse to confirm or deny my motivations.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.78,0:10:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\t(2500,4440,\c&H110E0E&\3c&H040910&)}Don't try and hide your fetishes.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll relax on the beach in the afternoon, and have barbecue for dinner.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.45,0:10:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, with full stomachs,\N we'll have fun with fireworks.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good chance for you to get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakua, Kyogyoku, say hello.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I thought this was a pain,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.72,0:10:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but as long as I'm here I plan to have fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you all.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you too, say hello.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.76,0:11:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, I bet it'll be a lot of fun!\N I can't wait to eat some barbecue!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Karon-san's as energetic as ever!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.49,0:11:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to be sure, this is a great chance for us to\N meet new people and strengthen our relationships.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.71,0:11:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think? Airo-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I have to say one way or the other, this feels like a bother to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate the heat.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.78,0:11:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, remember to \Nplay nice with your friends.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since when have you been my mother, Alice?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.04,0:11:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\t(4000,5420,\c&H110E0E&\3c&H040910&)}Oh my. You don’t have to call me your mother, "young lady" will do fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.96,0:11:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killer technique,\N Ultra No-Way-In-Hell Super Spike!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.51,0:11:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With an exceedingly lame attack name like that, there's no way you could defeat me, Karon!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miracle Hyper Jump-Powered Smash!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I did it!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think I couldn't stop it at this range...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Working part-time all night might be hard,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I haven't felt this kind of indignity since I was a hero!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How irritating!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.27,0:12:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Working part-time all night sure is hard.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you're tired, \Nyou can't summon any strength.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.00,0:12:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However. That physical \Nlimitation is a good thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.52,0:12:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Striving to reach new heights,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.93,0:12:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dealing with a body that refuses to do as it's told...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.63,0:12:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, your will may be broken harder than your body in the end, but even so!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buckling down and refusing to give in
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,creates its own kind of \Nlight at the end of the tunnel!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things aren't going to go as you expect.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.68,0:12:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's because you can't reach\N those heights that life is interesting!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.71,0:12:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first glance, you seemed dim-witted,\N and your speech appeared foolishly blunt,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you say can some rather deep things.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.49,0:13:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you start looking up to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.03,0:13:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I may be impertinent \Nand arrogant, but I like you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.52,0:13:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that we're friends, why don't we run off into the sunset together?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's midday as hell right now, but I concur!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.70,0:13:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did they learn that kind of meat-headed communication?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, just looking at them is sweltering.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my, isn't it a good thing?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:27.09,0:13:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blending bodies and heat, \Ntheir hearts move as one.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of communication is lovely!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-If you say so...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.50,0:13:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Of course, I also love the quiet bonding we are sharing right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are many ways of \Ninteracting with other people.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.14,0:13:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, there are so\N many people in this world!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reca-san, you have such a big heart.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As one would expect of a former princess.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.61,0:13:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are times where I can't quite say the same about myself
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's not good, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.02,0:14:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are the decorations all Rococo?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we decide on a Gothic style?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because I like swirly things!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airo-san, you're too picky about your scenery!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh—what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.09,0:14:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing works out best when you stick to the plan!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my, if you get that upset about it,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're just as bad as Karon-san!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely mistaken!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell Uro-kun about this!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.03,0:14:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful former heroes\N in swimsuits! And the ocean!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this paradise?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a peaceful scene!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, peaceful.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apart from you being here.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can't fit in with them, huh.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl... she reminds me a lot of how you were long ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's just like you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.67,0:15:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to Uro-san, \NKougyoku-chan is way, way cuter!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four-eyes, you're getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:19.29,0:15:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want things that are important to you to remain important.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't accept new things.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You become obstinate and close in on yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just like you!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say she's like me, but you shouldn't treat her that way.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't tease her.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe just a little.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.26,0:15:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does make me want to... stir things up.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything tastes better \Nwhen you eat outside!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uro, more alcohol.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're drinking too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.93,0:16:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku-san!\NPerfectly-done meat, just for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.24,0:16:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I've been aiming to talk to you since this afternoon,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I became too caught\N up frolicking with Hakua-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku-san, let's be friends too!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.33,0:16:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woah, rejected! I just got hit with a clear, outright rejection!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, it was your own fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, heroes sure have such bad manners, it's a problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Woah, from the witch too!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let this loud one be,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.21,0:16:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and let's relax and talk over there, just us two support characters.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a pain too.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oi, Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it already! You've \Ngot to try to communicate or—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "friends"?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "communication"?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you get along with them?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a hero, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you been so \Nunhappy about this whole time?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going out of their way to have fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's because of that that you're—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what\N my younger sister is thinking.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check on her.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.00,0:17:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unde ești?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alice went after her, so I'm sure it's nothing too extreme, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is something to \Nbe worried about, isn't it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's bound to be up to something,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:59.49,0:18:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that old monster.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.00,0:18:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She does tend to play \Nsome nasty tricks sometimes.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's overloaded with cuteness.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Uro.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sper că nu este supărată pe noi Kougyoku.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airo?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand her feelings.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.37,0:18:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As support characters, no matter how hard we try, we can't get the glory.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we get so\N picky about certain things.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's really important to her is probably...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She won't be mad.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hakua understands that too.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could Kougyoku-san be—
Dialogue: 100,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could she possibly be \Ntalking about, that sister of mine?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:01.48,0:19:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All my plans have gone down the drain!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hakua!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finished a new gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:17.73,0:19:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's full of protection!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you have this, you're invincible!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief, she's so troublesome!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.46,0:19:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Încă nu am reușit s-o găsim...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where did that meat-head go?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And four-eyes, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Karon-san's gone too, then that means...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.32,0:19:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it is Alice.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airo-san?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Reca! Stay close to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.89,0:20:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alice! Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.94,0:20:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We have the heroes. If you want them back, come to the beach!"
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamada Uro!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Send Hakua and me back to our world!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alice. What's this about?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just helping out a woman\N with something to say.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.98,0:20:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to test you, anytime, anywhere.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:57.80,0:21:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose I could get you to \Nstop putting my life on Hard Mode?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Send us back immediately!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kougyoku. You made that \Ncrossbow by yourself, didn't you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't shoot with that.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not held together well, and it's crooked.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but as long as \Nyou can't accept this world,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't craft anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taci!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu ce drept spui asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:23.55,0:21:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crafting things in this \Nworld is a very difficult thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as you're not looking\N properly at the things in front of you,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't make anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.97,0:21:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you get in my way?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:39.32,0:21:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just love the hero Hakua,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to make things for her
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.41,0:21:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she can be praised,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.36,0:21:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and free, and strong... that's all.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stupid little sister!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:04.37,0:22:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Become the greatest craftsperson in this world, \Ntoo! This time, without any magic!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakua...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:13.14,0:22:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning for a situation \Nwhere you were more excited,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:17.10,0:22:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that's not a big deal anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. It's a present for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:25.02,0:22:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakua's been working so hard at her part-time job to buy this for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:29.16,0:22:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Day in and day out, living a life she couldn't get used to...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:32.82,0:22:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can do anything if I put my mind to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why would you do something like that for me?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:41.26,0:22:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a supporting character.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my job to give you—
Dialogue: 100,0:22:45.59,0:22:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you being so\N picky about? Sister of mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received so much from \Nyou back in the other world.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time it's my turn to give.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:55.81,0:22:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earn money through dealing with people.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}I'll take on the daily tasks of a hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:01.41,0:23:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way you can put your whole \Nheart into mastering craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:06.16,0:23:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that means you—
Dialogue: 100,0:23:07.75,0:23:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the other world \NI was one of the greatest hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in this world...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:19.01,0:23:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm your only sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:30.20,0:23:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 100,0:23:31.15,0:23:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:33.56,0:23:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you ought to be a little fashionable too.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.93,0:23:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like me, you can't \Nlet your beauty go to waste.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:49.05,0:23:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:55.11,0:23:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:57.53,0:23:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară...
Dialogue: 100,0:24:11.68,0:24:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a sparkler!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:13.60,0:24:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, wait your turn!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:16.18,0:24:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl's just like you after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:18.82,0:24:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You keep saying that, but in what way?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:20.50,0:24:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever she decides something's important, she won't let go no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:24.76,0:24:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, very stubborn.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:26.61,0:24:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, when you put it that way, I kind of—
Dialogue: 100,0:24:29.36,0:24:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Karon! Don't wave the\N sparkler around! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:33.43,0:24:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody let me down...
Dialogue: 100,0:24:36.32,0:24:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that matter settled, it's so much fun to fireworks with everyone!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:41.46,0:24:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were easily captured \Npretty early on, weren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:45.08,0:24:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are the kind of witch that little kids worry about.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:48.82,0:24:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce ai spus?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:49.75,0:24:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide să mai aprindem una!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:50.77,0:24:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hei, așteaptă!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:54.14,0:24:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, am pierdut din nou!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:56.75,0:24:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ura, șapte la rând!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:58.82,0:25:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta e surioara mea!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:02.00,0:25:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu o voi pierde pe următoarea!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:03.70,0:25:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tot eu voi câștiga!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:05.04,0:25:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și voi face opt puncte!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:06.51,0:25:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce briză plăcută.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:49.35,0:25:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu credeți că există și lucruri \Nfrumoase în această lume?
Dialogue: 100,0:26:03.70,0:26:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ba da!
